蛇蛇／阿妤／以姓为傲，不以身贵而自满； Pride in surname, not in dignity and  complacency. 以策为重，不以浮躁而轻敌； Focus on policy, not in impetuosity and belittle the  enemy. 审时度势，明哲保身； Judging the situation at the right time and protecting  oneself wisely. 以荣利为重，以情长为轻； Emphasis should be placed on honor and  profit, and on affection. 言出必行，行之必果， Words must be done and deeds must be done. 不形喜怒于色，不求安康于贫。 Be indifferent to anger, not to seek well-being in  poverty.／／／／／2023-6-21